@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Land_O_Mines" where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries
are needed.

                             How to play?

  To play, just click on a space next to your current position (where the
smiling face icon is located), you can move horizontally, vertically or
diagonally. Each time you leave a tile, that tile disappears, so you
cannot go back there. Be careful not to 'trap' yourself on a tile with
no other tiles you can go to, in which case the game will be over.

  If one (or more) mine is adjacent to your position, all the surrounding
tiles, except the removed ones, will be marked by a '?' icon, but you
will never know exactly where a mine is located.
  
  When you complete a level, the game counts how many moves you made and
multiply it by the bonus for that level, so the more moves you make, the
higher the score you will get. That score will be added to the total
score in the game. But if you step on a mine or trap yourself, only the
number of moves will be added to the total score.

  At the end of every level, whether you completed it or not, the game
displays where the mines were located. The game will also display how
many moves you made on that level and the bonus (if any) with your total
score.

  Have fun!

